-- MOVES-Amundi hires Benedicte Rabier from Allenbridge Epic
-- 
-- Thu Dec 11, 2014 06:27AM EST
-- None



Dec 11 (Reuters) - Paris-based asset management company Amundi appointed Benedicte Rabier as senior product specialist of its alternative investments.

Rabier will be based in London and report to Michael Hart, deputy chief executive of the alternative investments business.